男子以 50 英镑聘用班克斯后，在他的壁画上作画：“我一点也不后悔” https://www.nme.com/news/music/man-speaks-out-after-hiring-banksy-for-50-then-painting-over-his-mural-i-have-no-regrets-at-全部-3829346？u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=男人在雇用班克斯 50 人后说出他的壁画，然后在他的壁画上绘画，我一点也不后悔Daniel PetersThu, 16 Jan 2025 03:12:18 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3829346 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="班克斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> “当时这只是另一个艺术项目”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/man-speaks-out-after-hiring-banksy-for-50-then-painting-over-his-mural-i-have-no-regrets-at-all-3829346">曼以 50 英镑聘请班克斯后发表言论，然后在他的壁画上绘画：“我一点也不后悔”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="班克斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Banksy-Mild_Mild_West-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>一名男子讲述了一段时期，他聘请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/banksy">班克斯 (Banksy)</a>举办一个艺术研讨会，花费 50 英镑，其中包括一幅壁画，然后将其涂掉。</p><p>布里斯托尔市议会资深从业者彼得·德波尔昨天（1月15日）接受了<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cql5dx1l9e9o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>采访，讲述了1990年代聘请班克斯（其身份仍匿名）在当地一家青年俱乐部参加艺术课程的事。</p><p>在这些课程中，班克斯向布里斯托尔青少年群体教授涂鸦，德波尔称这是一次“真正的合作”，他们“参与其中，享受乐趣并分享想法”。</p><p> “如果你看这些照片，你就能看到他与年轻人合作​​的方式，”德波尔告诉<em>英国广播公司</em>。该公司在保留班克斯匿名的条件下公布了这些课程的照片。</p><p>班克斯以 50 英镑的价格被聘请来与孩子们一起举办一个工作室，孩子们很高兴能与这位艺术家合作，尽管“没有人仔细考虑过他是谁”。</p><p> “当时让我印象深刻的是他并没有真正的自我。他是在和他们一起做艺术，而不是为他们做艺术，”德波尔透露。 “早上，他和孩子们围坐在一张桌子旁，谈论他们的想法。然后他们就会把这些发明的东西扔进去并喷洒。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE1p1p-NfjM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" f